# Festival Network — public site links

Human-facing pages in `docs/` publish to [cpalss.github.io/festival-network](https://cpalss.github.io/festival-network/). **GitHub Pages renders `docs/` only.**

Full policy: [ai-asset-conventions.md](../docs/ai-asset-conventions.md) § Public site links.

| Target | Use |
|--------|-----|
| Another site page | **`.html`** — e.g. `research.html`, `lny/market-research.html` |
| Repo file (`assets/`, `AGENTS.md`) | `https://github.com/cPALSs/festival-network/blob/main/...` |
| Coalition-internal monorepo | **Plain text** — no link |

**Never link:** `../assets/`, `../AGENTS.md`, `github.com/cPALSs/cPALSs/`, `Staff - Meeting/`, `Projects - …/`.

Before commit: grep `docs/` for `\]\(\.\./`, `cPALSs/cPALSs`, and site cross-links ending in `.md)`.
